Polymetal: Nesis Can Hold Posts of CEO, Director of Polymetal

-- B y   T o n y   B a r r e t t
-- 
2011-09-30T12:56:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/polymetal-nesis-can-hold-posts-of-ceo-director-of-polymetal.html
OAO Polymetal said the board of
directors approved that Vitaly Nesis, chief executive officer,
can simultaneously hold the post of CEO and director of
Polymetal International Plc. The company commented in a
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
